schools.name: Edmundo Eddie Escobedo Sr Middle School

data.description: Beautiful and immaculate two story home in desirable Providence community with no neighbors behind! The home has a spacious open floor plan. The living room features custom shelving, cozy custom paint, stunning dark tile flooring, and ceiling fan. The dining area has a gorgeous chandelier. The upgraded kitchen has stainless steel appliances, brand new dishwasher, dark cabinet, and granite countertops. Upstairs has a separate laundry room, desk area perfect for a cozy office, and 3 bedrooms. The primary bedroom is separate from the secondary. There's beautiful mountain views from the balcony off the primary bedroom. The primary bathroom has a separate shower and tub and spacious walk in closet. The secondary bedrooms have custom paint and access to second balcony. The backyard is perfect for entertaining with covered patio, outdoor kitchen including bbq and so much more. Must see home!
